data.description: SELLER MOTIVATED! Introducing 11439 Fulmar Rd., a charming property located in Weeki Wachee, Florida. This delightful home features a spacious layout with 4 bedrooms and 3.5 bathrooms, perfect for comfortable living. Situated on almost a full acre lot, this property offers ample outdoor space for relaxation, recreation and storage for all of your outdoor toys!    One of the standout features of this property is the convenient 50 & 30 amp RV hook-up, catering to your adventurous spirit and offering a seamless way to accommodate your recreational vehicle. Whether you're a road-trip enthusiast or simply value the flexibility of having an RV on hand, this feature adds an extra layer of convenience to your lifestyle.    Inside, the home boasts an open floor plan that enhances both functionality and aesthetics. The high ceilings further contribute to the appeal of this wonderful home. With its ideal location in Weeki Wachee, you'll have easy access to the beautiful Weeki Wachee River, ideal for kayaking, paddle boarding or even boating making it a desirable place to call home.    Don't miss the opportunity to make 11439 Fulmar Rd. your own—a property that combines comfort, functionality, and the freedom to embark on RV adventures right from your doorstep. Contact us today to schedule a viewing and experience all that this unique property has to offer.
